{
  "id": "69d0435132bc98cf8a9eec28",
  "title": "変な数詞・数体系",
  "created": 1775256403,
  "updated": 1775264832,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d0435132bc98cf8a9eec28",
      "text": "変な数詞・数体系",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256403,
      "updated": 1775256464
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04353000000000096c000",
      "text": "日本語母語話者からすると「変」に感じる数詞・数体系を探す",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256403,
      "updated": 1775256458
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04672000000000096c014",
      "text": "\t漢語の数体系がよく出来すぎている。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775257202,
      "updated": 1775257213
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0436a000000000096c002",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256427,
      "updated": 1775256427
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0436b000000000096c003",
      "text": "日本語の数体系",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256427,
      "updated": 1775256469
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04394000000000096c004",
      "text": "\tひとつ、ふたつ、みっつ、よっつ、いつつ、むっつ、ななつ、やっつ、ここのつ、とお",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256469,
      "updated": 1775256531
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0453b000000000096c00d",
      "text": "\t\tはた（20）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256891,
      "updated": 1775256898
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0436a000000000096c001",
      "text": " [https://www.eonet.ne.jp/~shiyokkyo/rizhong/kazu.html 日本語の数の数え方について   ―― 「大和言葉」とはどういうものか？]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256427,
      "updated": 1775256652
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04414000000000096c007",
      "text": "  > 更に言えば、どうも漢語到来以前の「日本語」（大和言葉）というか、列島の言語には、まだ11より上の数を数える言葉が存在していなかった。つまり、まだ11以上の数を認識する必要が出てくるほどには、列島の生活文化は発展しておらず、それが中国漢字文明の到来によって、ようやく11以上の数を認識する必要のある段階に達したのであり、それとともに、「十一・十二・十三・・・・」と漢語をそのまま用いたのではないかと考えるのである。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256597,
      "updated": 1775256603
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0441c000000000096c008",
      "text": "  えー……[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256604,
      "updated": 1775256613
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04467000000000096c00b",
      "text": "  \tテラの上や京の上をめったに使わないとかと同じようなものかな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256680,
      "updated": 1775256790
    },
    {
      "id": "69d044d7000000000096c00c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256791,
      "updated": 1775256946
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04571000000000096c00e",
      "text": "漢語の数体系",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256946,
      "updated": 1775258380
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04ab2000000000096c02c",
      "text": "\t小さいうちは十進法、大きくなると万進法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258291,
      "updated": 1775258302
    },
    {
      "id": "69d045a4000000000096c00f",
      "text": "\t[$ a]：零（れい）、一（いち）、二（に）、三（さん）、四（し）、五（ご）、六（ろく）、七（しち）、八（はち）、九（く、きゅう）、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256996,
      "updated": 1775257466
    },
    {
      "id": "69d045d3000000000096c011",
      "text": "\t[$ 10+a]：十（じゅう）、十一、～、十九",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775257043,
      "updated": 1775257387
    },
    {
      "id": "69d045d8000000000096c012",
      "text": "\t[$ a\\times10+b]：二十、二十一、～、二十九、～～、九十一、～、九十九",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775257049,
      "updated": 1775257839
    },
    {
      "id": "69d045e3000000000096c013",
      "text": "\t[$ 100+b]：百（ひゃく）、百一、～、百九十九",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775257059,
      "updated": 1775257955
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04411000000000096c006",
      "text": "\t[$ a\\times100+b]：二百（ひゃく）、二百一、～、九百九十九、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775256594,
      "updated": 1775257788
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04955000000000096c028",
      "text": "\t[$ 1000+b]：千、～、千一、～、千九百九十九",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775257942,
      "updated": 1775258021
    },
    {
      "id": "69d049a8000000000096c029",
      "text": "\t[$ a\\times1000+b]：二千、～、二千一、～、九千九百九十九",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258025,
      "updated": 1775258204
    },
    {
      "id": "69d049e0000000000096c02a",
      "text": "\t[$ a\\times10000+b]：一万、一万一、～、一万九千九百九十九、二万、二万一、～、九万九千九百九十九、～～～、九千九百九十九万九千九百九十九",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258080,
      "updated": 1775258213
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04a35000000000096c02b",
      "text": "\t[$ a\\times10^8+b]：一億、一億一、～、九千九百九十九億九千九百九十九万九千九百九十九",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258166,
      "updated": 1775258261
    },
    {
      "id": "69d047d0000000000096c016",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775257552,
      "updated": 1775257552
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04b12000000000096c030",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258386,
      "updated": 1775258386
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04b04000000000096c02e",
      "text": "英語の数体系",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258372,
      "updated": 1775258386
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04b13000000000096c031",
      "text": "\t[$ a]:  zero (0), one (1), two (2), three (3), four (4), five (5), six (6), seven (7), eight (8), nine (9), ten (10), eleven (11), twelve (12)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258387,
      "updated": 1775259152
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04b44000000000096c033",
      "text": "\t[$ a+10]:  thirteen (3+10), fourteen (4+10), fifteen (5+10), sixteen (6+10), seventeen (7+10), eighteen (8+10), nineteen (9+10)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258436,
      "updated": 1775259190
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04b95000000000096c034",
      "text": "\t[$ a\\times10+b]: twenty (2*10), twenty-one (2*10 + 1), ..., ninetey-nine (9*10 + 9)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258517,
      "updated": 1775259222
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04be3000000000096c035",
      "text": "\t[$ a\\times100+b]: one hundred (1*100), one hundred and one (1*100 + 1), ..., nine hundred and ninety-nine (9*100 + 9*10 + 9)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258596,
      "updated": 1775259259
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04d25000000000096c036",
      "text": "\t[$ a\\times1000+b]: one thousand (1*1,000), ..., nine hundred ninety-nine thousand nine hundred ninety-nine ({9*100 + 9*10 + 9} * 1,000  +  9*100 + 9*10 + 9)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258918,
      "updated": 1775259414
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04d55000000000096c037",
      "text": "\t[$ a\\times10^6+b]:  one million (1*1,000,000), ..., nine hundred ninety-nine million nine hundred ninety-nine thousand nine hundred ninety-nine ({9*100 + 9*10 + 9} * 1,000,000  +  {9*100 + 9*10 + 9} * 1,000  +  9*100 + 9*10 + 9)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258965,
      "updated": 1775259461
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04b04000000000096c02f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775258372,
      "updated": 1775258372
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04f83000000000096c038",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775259523,
      "updated": 1775259523
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04f84000000000096c03a",
      "text": "ローマ数字の数体系",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775259524,
      "updated": 1775259535
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05892000000000096c059",
      "text": "\t\t[ローマ数字の一覧]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261843,
      "updated": 1775261850
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05322000000000096c043",
      "text": "\t減算があるので複雑そうに見える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775260450,
      "updated": 1775260466
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05332000000000096c044",
      "text": "\t\t実際は IV を 5-1 として扱わずに 4 だと思うと見通しが良くなる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775260466,
      "updated": 1775260492
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0539b000000000096c047",
      "text": "\t\t同様に IX は 10-1 として扱わずに 9 だと思うと見通しが良くなる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775260571,
      "updated": 1775260571
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0539b000000000096c048",
      "text": "\t\t同様に XL は 50-10 として扱わずに 40 だと思うと見通しが良くなる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775260571,
      "updated": 1775260583
    },
    {
      "id": "69d053a8000000000096c04a",
      "text": "\t\t\tXLIX は 49",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775260585,
      "updated": 1775260591
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0534c000000000096c045",
      "text": "\t[$ a]:  I (1), II (1*2), III(1*3)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775260492,
      "updated": 1775260571
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04fd7000000000096c03c",
      "text": "\t[$ 5-1]: IV(5-1)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775259607,
      "updated": 1775259716
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0500d000000000096c03d",
      "text": "\t[$ 5+a]: V(5), VI(5+1), VII(5+1*2), VIII(5+1*3)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775259661,
      "updated": 1775259691
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05037000000000096c03e",
      "text": "\t[$ 10-1]: IX(10-1)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775259703,
      "updated": 1775259732
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05057000000000096c03f",
      "text": "\t[$ 10\\times a+b]: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775259736,
      "updated": 1775261078
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05595000000000096c04c",
      "text": "\t\tX(10), XI(10 + 1), XII(10 + 1*2), XIII(10 + 1*3), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261078,
      "updated": 1775261089
    },
    {
      "id": "69d055a1000000000096c04e",
      "text": "\t\tXIV(10 + {5 - 1}), XV(10 + 5), XVI(10 + {5 + 1}), XVII(10 + {5 + 1*2}), XVIII(10 + {5 + 1*3}), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261089,
      "updated": 1775261095
    },
    {
      "id": "69d055a7000000000096c04f",
      "text": "\t\tXIX(10 + {10 - 1}), XX(10*2), ..., XXXVIII(10*3 + 5 + 3), XXXIX(10*3 + {10-1})",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261095,
      "updated": 1775261096
    },
    {
      "id": "69d051b7000000000096c040",
      "text": "\t[$ (50-10)+a]: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775260087,
      "updated": 1775261619
    },
    {
      "id": "69d055b5000000000096c050",
      "text": " \tXL (50 - 10), XLI ({50 - 10} + 1), ... XLVIII ({50 - 10} + {5 + 3}), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261109,
      "updated": 1775261113
    },
    {
      "id": "69d055b9000000000096c051",
      "text": " \tXLIX ({50 - 10} + {10-1})",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261113,
      "updated": 1775261113
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05518000000000096c04b",
      "text": "\t[$ 50+b]: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775260952,
      "updated": 1775261145
    },
    {
      "id": "69d055d8000000000096c052",
      "text": " \tL(50), LI(50 + 1), LII(50 + 1*2), LIII(50 + 1*3), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261145,
      "updated": 1775261149
    },
    {
      "id": "69d055dc000000000096c053",
      "text": " \tLIV(50 + {5 - 1}), LV(50 + 5), LVI(50 + {5 + 1}), LVII(50 + {5 + 1*2}), LVIII(50 + {5 + 1*3})",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261149,
      "updated": 1775261187
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0561d000000000096c054",
      "text": " \tLIX(50 + {10-1}), LX(50 + 10), LXI(50 + 10 + 1), LXII(50 + 10 + 1*2), LXIII(50 + 10 + 1*3), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261213,
      "updated": 1775261365
    },
    {
      "id": "69d056bd000000000096c055",
      "text": " \tLXIV(50 + 10 + {5 - 1}), LXV(50 + 10 + 5), LXVI(50 + 10 + {5 + 1}), LXVII(50 + 10 + {5 + 1*2}), LXVIII(50 + 10 + {5 + 1*3}), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261374,
      "updated": 1775261433
    },
    {
      "id": "69d056fc000000000096c056",
      "text": " \tLXIX(50 + 10 + {10 - 1}), LXX(50 + 10*2), ..., LXXX(50 + 10*3), LXXXIX(50 + 10*3 + {10 - 1})",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261436,
      "updated": 1775261533
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05784000000000096c057",
      "text": " [$ (100-10)+b]:",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261572,
      "updated": 1775261611
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05790000000000096c058",
      "text": " \tXC(100 - 10), ..., XCIX({100 - 10} + (10 - 1))",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775261585,
      "updated": 1775261671
    },
    {
      "id": "69d04f83000000000096c039",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775259523,
      "updated": 1775259523
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05dc8000000000096c05a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775263176,
      "updated": 1775263176
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05dca000000000096c05c",
      "text": "フランス語の数体系",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775263178,
      "updated": 1775263183
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05dce000000000096c05d",
      "text": "\t[$ a]:  un/une(1), deux(2), trois(3), quatre(4), cinq(5), six(6), sept(7), huit(8), neuf(9), dix(10), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775263183,
      "updated": 1775263470
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05e9a000000000096c05e",
      "text": "\t[$ a+10]:  onze(1 + 10), douze(2 + 10), treize(3 + 10), quatroze(4 + 10), quinze(5 + 10), seize(6 + 10)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775263387,
      "updated": 1775263468
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05ee6000000000096c05f",
      "text": "\t[$ 10+a]:  dix-sept(10 + 7), dix-huit(10 + 8), dix-neuf(10 + 9)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775263462,
      "updated": 1775263506
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05f1a000000000096c060",
      "text": "\t[$ 20+a]:  vingt(20), vingt-et-un/une (20 + 1), vingt-deux (20 + 2), vingt-trois(20 + 3), vingt-quatre(20 + 4), vingt-cinq(20 + 5), vingt-six(20 + 6), vingt-sept(20 + 7), vingt-huit(20 + 8), vingt-neuf(20 + 9)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775263514,
      "updated": 1775263707
    },
    {
      "id": "69d05fdb000000000096c061",
      "text": "\t[$ a*10+b]:  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775263708,
      "updated": 1775263815
    },
    {
      "id": "69d06046000000000096c063",
      "text": "\t\ttrente(3*10), trente-et-un/une (3*10 + 1), trente-deux (3*10 + 2), trente-trois(3*10 + 3), trente-quatre(3*10 + 4), trente-cinq(3*10 + 5), trente-six(3*10 + 6), trente-sept(3*10 + 7), trente-huit(3*10 + 8), trente-neuf(3*10 + 9), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775263815,
      "updated": 1775263821
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0604a000000000096c064",
      "text": "\t\tquarante(4*10), quarante-et-un/une (4*10 + 1), quarante-deux (4*10 + 2), quarante-trois(4*10 + 3), quarante-quatre(4*10 + 4), quarante-cinq(4*10 + 5), quarante-six(4*10 + 6), quarante-sept(4*10 + 7), quarante-huit(4*10 + 8), quarante-neuf(4*10 + 9), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775263818,
      "updated": 1775263881
    },
    {
      "id": "69d0604a000000000096c065",
      "text": "\t\tcinquante(5*10), cinquante-et-un/une (5*10 + 1), cinquante-deux (5*10 + 2), cinquante-trois(5*10 + 3), cinquante-quatre(5*10 + 4), cinquante-cinq(5*10 + 5), cinquante-six(5*10 + 6), cinquante-sept(5*10 + 7), cinquante-huit(5*10 + 8), cinquante-neuf(5*10 + 9), ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
